      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUC9432d2182b87100583ac89ec0e3196d2"></a>Lubrication of the chain
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8606"> </a>O-ring chains have sealed, life-lubed link studs and bushes. However,&nbsp;these chains need lubricating at regular intervals to
            protect metal parts of the chain and the O-rings.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8608"> </a>Lubrication also serves to keep the O-rings soft and pliable to ensure the maximum sealing efficiency.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8610"> </a>Using a brush, apply a thin protective layer of high-density gearbox fluid along the entire length of the chain, both inside
            and outside.
         </div>
      </div>
